  "texts": [
    "This approach is in line with SDG 12.2.",
    "Sustainable cybersecurity in smart gridsWithin the electrical grid system, the evolution of the smart grid illustrates a significant shift toward integrating sustainable cybersecurity.",
    "This is crucial for ensuring the security, efficiency, and ecological impact of power delivery systems.",
    "The congressional report [51] focused on smart grid transformation and highlighted the integration of renewable energy sources (solar, wind).",
    "This modernization, including digital communication and information systems, enhances energy management and stability by leveraging advanced communication infrastructures, such as those integrating the IoT and cloud computing, which enable real-time data exchange for improved system resilience [93,94]."
